user.name: root
user.ObjectGrants: SELECT,INSERT,UPDATE,DELETE,CREATE,DROP,RELOAD,SHUTDOWN,PROCESS,FILE,REFERENCES,INDEX,ALTER,SHOW DATABASES,SUPER,CREATE TEMPORARY TABLES,LOCK TABLES,EXECUTE,REPLICATION SLAVE,REPLICATION CLIENT,CREATE VIEW,SHOW VIEW,CREATE ROUTINE,ALTER ROUTINE,CREATE USER,EVENT,TRIGGER,CREATE TABLESPACE,CREATE ROLE,DROP ROLE!

table.name: payment_type_record
table.Comment: 用户支付方式绑定记录表

column.name: audit_status
column.Comment: 审核状态0待审核1审核通过2不通过

column.name: Status
column.Comment: 0 手续费未到账 1 手续费已到账 2 已归集

column.name: Address
column.Comment: 归集地址（前端需要加密）

column.name: MainAddress
column.Comment: 提现私钥需要前端加密

column.name: IsAutoWithDraw
column.Comment: 是否开启自动提现（不建议开启）

column.name: MemoAddress
column.Comment: 用户填写备注码充值的地址 如果不需要填空

index.name: uk_cname_p
index.Comment: 同币种同协议只存在一条

column.name: status
column.Comment: 状态 0 禁用 1 启用

column.name: max_trading_order
column.Comment: 最大允许同时交易的订单数，0表示不限制

column.name: max_trading_time
column.Comment: 委托超时自动下架时间，单位为秒，0表示不过期

column.name: publish_type
column.Comment: 发行活动类型 1:无活动,2:抢购发行,3:分摊发行

column.name: level
column.Comment: 等级 0普通 1合约矿工 2节点矿工 3高级矿工 4超级矿工 5矿池

column.name: type
column.Comment: 奖励类型 0佣金 1推荐奖励

column.name: buy_min_amount
column.Comment: 买入广告最低发布数量

column.name: sell_min_amount
column.Comment: 卖出广告最低发布数量

column.name: Agreen
column.Comment: 0 为正常区块记录 1 后台增加

column.name: Status
column.Comment: 0 未到账 1 已到账 -1 失败

column.name: ProcessMold
column.Comment: *处理模式，0区块处理，1外部处理

column.name: Status
column.Comment: *状态，-1,驳回,0待处理,1处理中,2已处理 3 失败

column.name: WithdrawInfo
column.Comment: 提现失败原因（后台驳回理由可填写）
